Vulpix

Evolves At 4

Snow Warning

Passive Ability

Causes snow to fall on an enemy, dealing damage to it and decreasing their movement speed by 30% for .75s. This ability has a 4s cooldown. Boosted attacks, Snow Warning, and all moves (except Aurora Veil) sling snow; hitting the same target with snow 4 times will freeze them for 1s.

60% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 100

Attack

Auto Attack

Becomes a boosted attack with every third attack. When this boosted attack hits, it deals damage to nearby enemies and decreases their movement speed for a short time.

100% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

53.2% SpA + 13 x (Level - 1) + 250

Powder Snow

Move 1

5.00s Area

Ninetales attacks with a chilly gust of powdery snow; dealing damage to enemies hit and decreasing their movement speed by 50% for 1s.

78% SpA + 13 x (Level - 1) + 240

Powder Snow Upgrade Choices

Avalanche

7.50s Area

Ninetales attacks with a gust of chilly ice toward the designated direction. The ice damages enemies and forms a wall that can't be walked through. After a short time, this wall melts and collapses; further damaging enemies in a radius around the wall.

36% SpA + 8 x (Level - 1) + 190

Also decreases the movement speed of enemies by 50% for 1s when this move hits.

Dazzling Gleam

7.50s Hindrance

Ninetales attacks with a powerful cone of blinding light; damaging and stunning enemies hit for .8s.

60% SpA + 10 x (Level - 1) + 320

Increased damage and stun duration to 1s.

61% SpA + 10 x (Level - 1) + 380

Icy Wind

Move 2

8.00s Ranged

Attacks with a gust of freezing air; damaging, and slowing Pokémon hit by 20% for 1s. Icy Wind shoves Pokémon hit in the direction of the wind for a short distance unless they are already at the maximum range of the move.

61% SpA + 7 x (Level - 1) + 240

Icy Wind Upgrade Choices

Blizzard

7.50s Ranged

Ninetales blasts twice in a line. The first blast penetrates walls and slows enemies. The second blast deals double damage, shoves enemies back, and if it hits a wall it creates a frost area at the impact location for 4s; dealing damage every 0.5s and slowing enemies in the area by 35% for 1s on each tick.

39% SpA + 4 x (Level - 1) + 250

Deals twice the damage of the first hit.
78% SpA + 8 x (Level - 1) + 500

17% SpA + 2 x (Level - 1) + 110

Increased damage.

41% SpA + 6 x (Level - 1) + 270

Deals twice the damage of the first hit.
82% SpA + 12 x (Level - 1) + 540

18% SpA + 3 x (Level - 1) + 115

Aurora Veil

13.00s Buff

Ninetales dashes a short distance and creates an aurora centered on their position for 5s; reducing damage received by Ninetales and allies within the veil by 35%, healing Ninetales with each boosted attack, and increasing Attack Speed by 15%. While Ninetales is inside the aurora, movement speed is increased by 10% and all auto attacks are boosted.

10% SpA + 2 x (Level - 1) + 40

Damage reduction increased to 40% and cooldown reduced by 2s.

Snow Globe

Unite Move

112s 100000 Area

Unlocks at level 9

Attack with a chilly blast of snow and ice; dealing damage to enemies in the area of effect around Ninetales when it hits. Deals increased damage to enemies that are frozen. Ninetales is unstoppable during the cast.

224% SpA + 32 x (Level - 1) + 1520

156.8% SpA + 30 x (Level - 1) + 1064

Unite Buffs (6s duration):

30% Movement Speed, 30% CDR, 20% Max HP Shield
